                  <div class="entry">
                    <p>
                      Ben Simon implements the <a
                        href="http://schemepetstore.pbwiki.com/"
                        >Java Petstore in Scheme</a
                      > using the excellent <a
                        href="http://siscweb.sourceforge.net/news.html"
