                        href="http://sisc.sourceforge.net/">SISC</a
                      > Scheme implementation. Well worth a look, particularly
                      the<a
                        href="http://schemepetstore.pbwiki.com/f/writeup.pdf"
                        >writeup</a
                      > which explains some of the advantages Scheme brings to
                      web development.
                    </p>
